title: Six Cents And Natalie
description:
Artist Description:

Six Cents and Natalie is the sporadic side-project of Tullycraft lead singer Sean Tollefson. This lo-fi band actually predates his pre-Tullycraft band Crayon. Six Cents and Natalie released a series of cassette tapes and 7" singles, and eventually released two full length CDs.
